Package: ncaaStatsSync
Type: Package
Title: NCAA D3 Player and Team Stat Sync
Version: 0.4.5
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Trafton",
      family = "OBrien",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "maintainers@example.com"
    )
  )
Description: Fetches NCAA Division III season-to-date stats via a shared browser
    session, parses pitching and batting player tables, computes derived metrics
    (FIP, wRC+, WAR-style summaries), aggregates team-level and qualified-team
    summaries, and writes deterministic JSON for downstream apps or scheduled
    GitHub Actions.
